entries.title: GeForce Now upgrades to RTX 4080 for 4K 240Hz cloud gaming
entries.description: Nvidia GeForce Now has just received a major upgrade -- you can soon try out cloud gaming on an RTX 4080.

entries.title: Nvidia brings the mighty RTX 4090 to laptops at CES 2023
entries.description: Laptop gamers, get ready -- Nvidia has just announced the upcoming release of its RTX 40-series mobile graphics cards.

entries.title: CES 2023: Intel’s new 13th-gen CPUs are faster, cheaper, and more efficient
entries.description: Intel has just unveiled a massive list of new desktop processors, including some ultra-efficient chips that cost less than the K-series models.
